 Consider what 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{P}_{i}^{(\alpha)}$
\end_inset

 does to one of thes partner functions.)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Prove that the sum of the projection operators 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{P}^{(\alpha)}$
\end_inset

