\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

 gives 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{\alpha}\hat{P}^{(\alpha)}=\sum_{\alpha,i}\hat{P}_{i}^{(\alpha)}=1$
\end_inset

 (the identity operator), by using the column-orthogonality property of
 the character table.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
